{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji34.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给黄炎培的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给黄炎培的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1954年11月23日）任之先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月三十日惠书收到。购粮事，我在京所闻，亦如先生所述。来广州时沿途调查，始知问题仍是有的，但一般尚好，据说比去年要好得多。“五反”余案，已请陈云副总理注意。尊恙如何甚念，尚希注意护养。此复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年十一月廿三日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]黄炎培，字任之，当时任中国民主建国会主任委员、全国人大常委会副委员长。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1954,"month":11,"day":23}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":349,"page_end":349},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}